arted with one course and now have seven courses on our scope and further approved to deliver 20 related skill sets, which speak of our continuous growth and respect earned from students, regulatory organizations and related industries.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\nThe mission of Optimistic Futures is to contribute to regional Victorian economy by providing quality training to fulfil gap between industry demands and qualified skilled worker.<br />\r\nAs part of continuous growth, we are continuously looking to expand our scope as our aim is to meet market gap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade in\" id=\"menu7\">\r\n<h3>Fees Schedule</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"#\" src=\"./assets/frontend/front-pages/images/CMGF.png\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease check your eligibility at:<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.skills.vic.gov.au/victorianskillsgateway/Students/Pages/vtg-eligibility-indicator.aspx?Redirect=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.skills.vic.gov.au/victorianskillsgateway/Students/Pages/vtg-eligibility-indicator.aspx?Redirect=1</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nor alternatively please call our office for further information.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadmeadows Branch</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>9 Central Grove Broadmeadows 3047<br />\r\nT: (03) 9309 3370</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Glenroy Branch</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>4 Lytton St Glenroy 3046<br />\r\nT: (03) 9917 2133</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Shepparton Branch</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>54 MacIntosh St, Shepparton<br />\r\nT: (03) 5821 8665</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- tag_area--></div>\r\n<!-- search_area_sub--></div>\r\n<!-- search_area--><!--SEARCH AREA END--><!--CONTENT AREA START-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"body_content\">\r\n<div class=\"body_content_sub\">\r\n<h1 class=\"my_h1_center\">Find A Course</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"style4\" /><!-- HR LINE-->\r\n<div class=\"media my_content\"><img alt=\"...\" class=\"mr-3 mobile_image\" src=\"./assets/frontend/front-pages/images/search_indi.jpg\" />\r\n<div class=\"med