             </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Security Operations</a>\r\n                <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"cpp20212.html\">CPP20212 Cert II</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"cpp30411.html\">CPP30411 Cert III</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"brochure-baton-handcuffs.html\">Baton & Handcuff</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"control-rooms.html\">Control Room</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Early Childhood Education and Care</a>\r\n                 <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"chc30113.html\">CHC30113 Cert III</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"chc50113.html\">CHC50113 Diploma</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Emergency First Aid</a>\r\n                 <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid001.html\">HLTAID001</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid002.html\">HLTAID002</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid003.html\">HLTAID003</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid004.html\">HLTAID004</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </div>\r\n        <div class=\"tab-content py-3 px-3 px-sm-0\" id=\"nav-coursesContent\">\r\n          \r\n          <!-- Individual panal starts here -->\r\n          <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"nav-about\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"nav-home-tab\">\r\n            <section class=\"course_banner\" style=\"background-image: url(\'./uploads/pages/emg_aid.jpg\');\">\r\n              \r\n              <aside class=\"course_banner_content\">\r\n                <!-- <img src=\"./uploads/pages/course_contect_banner.jpg\"> -->\r\n                <div class=\"col-my-8\">\r\n<h2 class=\"tab_course_titles\">EMERGENCY FIRST AID</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"tab_course_titles\">COURSE | OPTIMISTICFUTURES</h2>\r\n                  <p class=\"tab_course_para\">We prepare you to deal with the realities of emergency situations. First aid skills and competencies are some of the most important things anyone can ever learn. In the case of an accident or critical health incident, it takes a confident and knowledgeable employee/person to be able to provide that first aid response care that can either save a life, or dramatically improve the outcome for the patient.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-my-4\">\r\n                    <a href=\"pdf/HLTAID001.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"application_submit_form_download\">Download Brochure</a>\r\n                    <a href=\"login.html\" class=\"application_submit_form\">Application Form</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </aside>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <div class=\"panel-group\" id=\"accordion_single\">\r\n              <div class=\"panel panel-default\">\r\n                <div class=\"row\">\r\n                  \r\n                  <!-- first two of individual starts here -->\r\n                  <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <ul class=\"course_lists\">\r\n                      <li><p>Course code: HLTAID001</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Course name: Provide cardiopulmonary resuscitation</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Release: 5</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Study area: Resuscitation</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Location: 4 Lytton street Glenroy, 3046</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Duration: 1 days</p></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse1\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Introduction </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>HLTAID001 Provide cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) is for both new learners and those refreshing their existing skills. It is recommended that Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation (CPR) is updated every 12 months.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>This short course is specifically designed to provide students with the knowledge to perform CPR in line with the Australian Resuscitation Council Guidelines. Areas covered include introduction to first aid principles, airway and breathing management and cardiopulmonary resuscitation and defibrillation.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>Students will be required to demonstrate that they have the required knowledge and skills necessary to manage an unconscious, non-breathing casualty to the arrival of medical aid.</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse2\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Pre-Requisites/Entry Requirements </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <ul class=\"Listing_view\">\r\n                          <li>There are no qualification pre-requisites for this course</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be aged 16 years or older</li>\r\n                          <li>Photo Identification is required to be sited prior to course commencement</li>\r\n                          <li>Language, literacy and numeracy skills</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be physically capable of bending and kneeling to provide first aid to a person on the floor. This includes performing CPR for up to 5 minutes.</li>\r\n                          <li>Completed enrolment form</li>\r\n                          <li>Payment of the course cost</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse3\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Mode of Delivery </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <p>Delivery of this course will be trainer led, face to face in a classroom setting combined with skills practice assessment.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse4\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Duration </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                         <p>The course duration for HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation is over 1 day</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse5\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Location </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       <p>Optimistic Futures: 4 Lytton street Glenroy 3046</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse6\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Commencement Dates </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>Course dates and times do vary. Please call us for more information on dates scheduled or alternately check our website <a href=\"http://www.optimisticfutures.com.au\">www.optimisticfutures.com.au</a></p>\r\n                        \r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                  </div>\r\n\r\n                  <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse7\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Materials </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse7\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n\r\n                       <p>Learner training is supported through the provision of quality learning materials and resources. Learners should attend the course in comfortable appropriate clothing. All equipment and consumable is supplied as part of the course</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse8\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Assessment Summary </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse8\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                          <p>The student will be assessed by demonstrating procedure applicable to this unit. They will also be required to answer a number of oral and written questions regarding their actions and theoretical application of knowledge. The assessment will also be part of a simulated activity set by the assessor. This activity must be conducted by an assessor or Optimistic Futures and must be completed in the workplace or in another environment that accurately simulates the workplace. The assessor is too actively set tasks for the student and must observe these tasks being performed.</p>\r\n\r\n                          <p>To standardise the application of the assessment, the assessment tasks (required skills and knowledge) are based on those specified in the Unit of Competency, HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation The assessor will use an assessment instrument mapped accordingly to the assessment requirements of this unit of competency. Assessors will apply an assessment procedure to ensure you are ready for the assessment and have the right resources and equipment to achieve the right standard.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                     <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse9\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Topics </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse9\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <ul class=\"Listing_view\">\r\n                          <li>The DDRSABCD Action Plan</li>\r\n                          <li>Managing unconscious casualties</li>\r\n                          <li>Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation (CPR)</li>\r\n                          <li>Using on Automated External Defibrillator</li>\r\n                          <li>Legal issues</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse10\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> National Recognition </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse10\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       <p>A certificate will be awarded upon successful completion of the unit; HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>This unit of competence is nationally recognised and provides individuals with a valuable outcome that can be applied throughout Australia.</p