s and those refreshing their existing skills. It is recommended that Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation (CPR) is updated every 12 months.</p>                          <p>This short course is specifically designed to provide students with the knowledge to perform CPR in line with the Australian Resuscitation Council Guidelines. Areas covered include introduction to first aid principles, airway and breathing management and cardiopulmonary resuscitation and defibrillation.</p>                          <p>Students will be required to demonstrate that they have the required knowledge and skills necessary to manage an unconscious, non-breathing casualty to the arrival of medical aid.</p>                        </div>                     </div>                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse2\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Pre-Requisites/Entry Requirements </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                         <ul class=\"Listing_view\">                           <li>There are no qualification pre-requisites for this course</li>                           <li>Learners must be aged 16 years or older</li>                           <li>Photo Identification is required to be sited prior to course commencement</li>                           <li>Language, literacy and numeracy skills</li>                           <li>Learners must be physically capable of bending and kneeling to provide first aid to a person on the floor. This includes performing CPR for up to 5 minutes.</li>                           <li>Completed enrolment form</li>                           <li>Payment of the course cost</li>                         </ul>                       </div>                     </div>                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse3\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Mode of Delivery </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                         <p>Delivery of this course will be trainer led, face to face in a classroom setting combined with skills practice assessment.</p>                       </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse4\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Duration </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                          <p>The course duration for HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation is over 1 day</p>                       </div>                     </div>                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse5\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Location </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                        <p>Optimistic Futures: 4 Lytton street Glenroy 3046</p>                       </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse6\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Commencement Dates </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                                                  <p>Course dates and times do vary. Please call us for more information on dates scheduled or alternately check our website <a href=\"http://www.optimisticfutures.com.au\">www.optimisticfutures.com.au</a></p>                                                </div>                     </div>                                                                             <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse7\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Materials </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse7\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                         <p>Learner training is supported through the provision of quality learning materials and resources. Learners should attend the course in comfortable appropriate clothing. All equipment and consumable is supplied as part of the course</p>                        </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse8\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Assessment Summary </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse8\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                           <p>The student will be assessed by demonstrating procedure applicable to this unit. They will also be required to answer a number of oral and written questions regarding their actions and theoretical application of knowledge. The assessment will also be part of a simulated activity set by the assessor. This activity must be conducted by an assessor or Optimistic Futures and must be completed in the workplace or in another environment that accurately simulates the workplace. The assessor is too actively set tasks for the student and must observe these tasks being performed.</p>                            <p>To standardise the application of the assessment, the assessment tasks (required skills and knowledge) are based on those specified in the Unit of Competency, HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation The assessor will use an assessment instrument mapped accordingly to the assessment requirements of this unit of competency. Assessors will apply an assessment procedure to ensure you are ready for the assessment and have the right resources and equipment to achieve the right standard.</p>                       </div>                     </div>                        <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse9\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Topics </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse9\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                                                  <ul class=\"Listing_view\">                           <li>The DDRSABCD Action Plan</li>                           <li>Managing unconscious casualties</li>                           <li>Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation (CPR)</li>                           <li>Using on Automated External Defibrillator</li>                           <li>Legal issues</li>                         </ul>                        </div>                     </div>                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse10\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> National Recognition </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse10\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                        <p>A certificate will be awarded upon successful completion of the unit; HLTAID001- Cardio- Pulmonary Resuscitation.</p>                          <p>This unit of competence is nationally recognised and provides individuals with a valuable outcome that can be applied throughout Australia.</p>                       </div>                     </div>                        <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse10\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Fees and Charges </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse10\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                        <p>Information about fees and charges is provided in the schedule of fees and charges which will have been included in your pre-enrolment information package. The basic course fees are: $65 per person.</p>                       </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse12\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Payment method </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse12\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                         <p>TEftpos and Cash</p>                       </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse13\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> We also deliver the following courses </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse13\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">                       <div class=\"panel-body\">                         <ul class=\"Listing_view\">                           <li>CHC30113- Certificate III in Early Childhood Education and Care</li>                           <li>CHC50113- Diploma of Early Childhood Education and Care</li>                           <li>CPP20212- Certificate II in Security Operations</li>                           <li>CPP30411- Certificate III in Security Operations</li>                         </ul>                       </div>                     </div>                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">                       <h4 class=\"panel-title\">                         <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse14\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Responsibility for Training </a>                       </h4>                     </div>                     <div id=\"collapse14\" c