    </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>Previously known as Apply first aid or Senior first aid, this training course will give you the skills and knowledge required to provide First Aid response, life support, management of casualty(s), the incident and other first aiders, in a range of situations, including in the home, workplace or within the community, until the arrival of medical or other assistance.</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse2\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Pre-Requisites/Entry Requirements </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <ul class=\"Listing_view\">\r\n                          <li>There are no qualification pre-requisites for this course</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be aged 16 years or older</li>\r\n                          <li>Photo Identification is required to be sited prior to course commencement</li>\r\n                          <li>Language, literacy and numeracy skills</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be physically capable of bending and kneeling to provide first aid to a person on the floor. This includes performing CPR for up to 5 minutes.</li>\r\n                          <li>Completed enrolment form</li>\r\n                          <li>Payment of the course cost</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse3\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Mode of Delivery </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <p>Delivery of this course will be trainer led, face to face in a classroom setting combined with skills practice assessment.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse4\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Duration </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                         <p>The course duration for HLTAID003- Provide First Aid is over 2 day</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse5\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Location </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       <p>Optimistic Futures: 4 Lytton street Glenroy 3046</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse6\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Commencement Dates </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>Course dates and times do vary. Please call us for more information on dates scheduled or alternately check our website <a href=\"http://www.optimisticfutures.com.au\">www.optimisticfutures.com.au</a></p>\r\n                        \r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                  </div>\r\n\r\n                  <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse7\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Materials </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse7\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n\r\n                       <p>Learner training is supported through the provision of quality learning materials and resources. Learners should attend the course in comfortable appropriate clothing. All equipment and consumable is supplied as part of the course</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse8\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Assessment Summary </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse8\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                          <p>The student will be assessed by demonstrating procedure applicable to this unit. They will also be required to answer a number of oral and written questions regarding their actions and theoretical application of knowledge. The assessment will also be part of a simulated activity set by the assessor. This activity must be conducted by an assessor or Optimistic Futures and must be completed in the workplace or in another environment that accurately simulates the workplace. The assessor is too actively set tasks for the student and must observe these tasks being performed.</p>\r\n\r\n                          <p>To standardise the application of the assessment, the assessment tasks (required skills and knowledge) are based on those specified in the Unit of Competency, HLTAID003- Provide First Aid The assessor will use an assessment instrument mapped accordingly to the assessment requirements of this unit of competency. Assessors will apply an assessment procedure to ensure you are ready for the assessment and have the right resources and equipment to achieve the right standard.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                     <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse9\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Topics </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n  