         <li><a href=\"individual-support.html\">CHC33015 Cert III</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Security Operations</a>\r\n                <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"cpp20212.html\">CPP20212 Cert II</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"cpp30411.html\">CPP30411 Cert III</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"brochure-baton-handcuffs.html\">Baton & Handcuff</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"control-rooms.html\">Control Room</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Early Childhood Education and Care</a>\r\n                 <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"chc30113.html\">CHC30113 Cert III</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"chc50113.html\">CHC50113 Diploma</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n              <li>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">Emergency First Aid</a>\r\n                 <ul class=\"second_sub_nav\">\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid001.html\">HLTAID001</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid002.html\">HLTAID002</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid003.html\">HLTAID003</a></li>\r\n                  <li><a href=\"hltaid004.html\">HLTAID004</a></li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n              </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </div>\r\n        <div class=\"tab-content py-3 px-3 px-sm-0\" id=\"nav-coursesContent\">\r\n          \r\n          <!-- Individual panal starts here -->\r\n          <div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"nav-about\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"nav-home-tab\">\r\n            <section class=\"course_banner\" style=\"background-image: url(\'./uploads/pages/emg_aid.jpg\');\">\r\n              \r\n              <aside class=\"course_banner_content\">\r\n                <!-- <img src=\"./uploads/pages/course_contect_banner.jpg\"> -->\r\n                <div class=\"col-my-8\">\r\n<h2 class=\"tab_course_titles\">EMERGENCY FIRST AID</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"tab_course_titles\">COURSE | OPTIMISTICFUTURES</h2>\r\n                  <p class=\"tab_course_para\">We prepare you to deal with the realities of emergency situations. First aid skills and competencies are some of the most important things anyone can ever learn. In the case of an accident or critical health incident, it takes a confident and knowledgeable employee/person to be able to provide that first aid response care that can either save a life, or dramatically improve the outcome for the patient.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-my-4\">\r\n                    <a href=\"pdf/HLTAID001.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"application_submit_form_download\">Download Brochure</a>\r\n                    <a href=\"login.html\" class=\"application_submit_form\">Application Form</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </aside>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <div class=\"panel-group\" id=\"accordion_single\">\r\n              <div class=\"panel panel-default\">\r\n                <div class=\"row\">\r\n                  \r\n                  <!-- first two of individual starts here -->\r\n                  <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <ul class=\"course_lists\">\r\n                      <li><p>Course code: HLTAID004</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Course name: Provide an emergency first aid response in an education and care setting</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Release: 5</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Study area: First aid</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Location: 4 Lytton street Glenroy, 3046</p></li>\r\n                      <li><p>Duration: 2 days</p></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n\r\n                       <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse29\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  HLTAID004 Provide an emergency first aid response in an education and care setting </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse29\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>We prepare you to deal with the realities of emergency situations. First aid skills and competencies are some of the most important things anyone can ever learn. In the case of an accident or critical health incident, it takes a confident and knowledgeable employee/person to be able to provide that first aid response care that can either save a life, or dramatically improve the outcome for the patient.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>First aid training comes in handy for a variety of different situations in life. Although many people receive this training strictly due to a job requirement, it is actually something that can benefit anyones life. Whether you need to become certified in emergency techniques as a part of your job or simply because youd like to be of assistance to others, you should have no problem accomplishing your goal with Optimistic Futures.</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse1\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Introduction </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>Optimistic Futures Pty Ltd is a registered training Organisation registered with the Australian Skills Quality Authority. Optimistic Futures is proud to offer training in HLTAID004 Provide an Emergency first aid response in an education setting.</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse2\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  Course Description </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <p>This course providers learner with the skills and knowledge required to provide first aid and is designed to meet the requirements from the HLT Health training package. Learners will understand how to respond to an emergency situation, apply first aid procedure and communicate the details of an incident to relevant personal. Additionally, you will also recognise the need to evaluate the incident and your own performance.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>This course is essential for people who are required to be able to provide first aid if an emergency situation arises in the course of their employment, or everyday life.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>This course prepares learners to understand to undertake the assessment to obtain a Statement of Attainment in HLTAI004- Provide an emergency first aid response in an education and care setting.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse3\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Pre-Requisites/Entry Requirements </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <ul class=\"Listing_view\">\r\n                          <li>There are no qualification pre-requisites for this course</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be aged 16 years or older</li>\r\n                          <li>Photo Identification is required to be sited prior to course commencement</li>\r\n                          <li>Language, literacy and numeracy skills</li>\r\n                          <li>Learners must be physically capable of bending and kneeling to provide first aid to a person on the floor. This includes performing CPR for up to 5 minutes.</li>\r\n                          <li>Completed enrolment form</li>\r\n                          <li>Payment of the course cost</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse4\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  Mode of Delivery </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                         <p>Delivery of this course will be trainer led, face to face in a classroom setting combined with skills practice assessment.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse5\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  Course Duration </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       <p>The course duration for HLTAID004- Provide an emergency first aid response in an education and care setting is over 2 days</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse6\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  Course Location </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                        <p>Optimistic Futures: 4 Lytton street Glenroy 3046</p>\r\n                        \r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                  </div>\r\n\r\n                  <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse7\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Commencement Dates </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse7\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n\r\n                       <p>Course dates and times do vary. Please call us for more information on dates scheduled or alternately check our website <a href=\"#\">www.optimisticfutures.com.au</a></p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse8\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Materials </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse8\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                          <p>Learner training is supported through the provision of quality learning materials and resources. Learners should attend the course in comfortable appropriate clothing. All equipment and consumable is supplied as part of the course</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                     <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse9\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  Assessment Summary </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse9\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        \r\n                       <p>The student will be assessed by demonstrating procedure applicable to this unit. They will also be required to answer a number of oral and written questions regarding their actions and theoretical application of knowledge. The assessment will also be part of a simulated activity set by the assessor. This activity must be conducted by an assessor or Optimistic Futures and must be completed in the workplace or in another environment that accurately simulates the workplace. The assessor is too actively set tasks for the student and must observe these tasks being performed.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>To standardise the application of the assessment, the assessment tasks (required skills and knowledge) are based on those specified in the Unit of Competency, HLTAID004- Provide an emergency first aid response in an education care setting. The assessor will use an assessment instrument mapped accordingly to the assessment requirements of this unit of competency. Assessors will apply an assessment procedure to ensure you are ready for the assessment and have the right resources and equipment to achieve the right standard.</p>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse40\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Course Topics </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse40\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       \r\n                        <ul class=\"Listing_view\">\r\n                          <li>Recognise an emergency situation</li>\r\n                          <li>Apply appropriate first aid procedure</li>\r\n                          <li>Perform CPR in accordance with ARC guidelines</li>\r\n                          <li>Display respectful behaviour</li>\r\n                          <li>Operate AED</li>\r\n                          <li>Communicate details</li>\r\n                          <li>Evaluate the incident and your own performance</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse10\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i>  National Recognition </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse10\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                       <p>A certificate will be awarded upon successful completion of the unit; HLTAID004- Provide an emergency first aid response in an education and care setting.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <p>This unit of competence is nationally recognised and provides individuals with a valuable outcome that can be applied throughout Australia.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#accordion_single\" href=\"#collapse12\" class=\"show_plus\"><i class=\"more-less glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></i> Fees and Charges </a>\r\n                      </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div id=\"collapse12\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse in\">\r\n                      <div class=\"panel-body\">\r\n                        <p>Information about fees and charges is provided in the schedule of fees and charges which will have been included in your pre-enrolment information package. The basic course fees are: $150 per person.</p>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"panel-heading\">\r\n                      <h4 class=\"panel-title\">\r\n                        <a data-toggle=\"collapse\" da